'''Frederick Giles Gibbs''' (31 October 1866&ndash;16 January 1953) was a New Zealand school principal, educationalist, businessman, naturalist and community leader. He was born in [[London]], [[London]], [[England]] on 31 October 1866.<ref name="DNZB Gibbs">{{DNZB|title=Frederick Giles Gibbs|first= Shirley|last= Tunnicliff|id=3g6|accessdate=23 April 2017}}</ref>

